Great is YOUR faithfulness towards us. #HeresTo3 🥂#Grace #Taylor #November2023 #GirlDad

Today, I want to take a moment to honor the woman who has seamlessly woven herself into every area of my life - my wife. 

You are the epitome of grace, patience and love and you are the quiet strength that propels me forward. 
I’ve told you in private but publicly I say, I do not know where I would be without you by my side. Through the thick & thin you have always continued to show that grace, patience and love.

So here’s to you, my love. Thank you for being the incredible woman that you are, for standing by me this year and loving me, even on the days I found it hard to love myself. 

You are the unsung hero of our story. 

With love,
 
William

I’ve learned that true transformation begins from within. It’s not just about changing our outer appearance or achieving certain milestones; it’s about nurturing our souls, expanding our minds, and cultivating a genuine sense of self-love and acceptance. I’ve delved into the depths of my being, untangling the knots of self-doubt and insecurities, and gradually unraveling the true essence of who I am.

“When Men Mend Everyone Wins” 
@iammiketodd - thank you Mike for this 💯
